	&lt;li&gt;USPTO/TrademarkStatusApp: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/USPTO/TrademarkStatusApp&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://github.com/USPTO/TrademarkStatusApp&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
